Key Match Events: Romain Saïss scored the opening goal in the first half.
Azzedine Ounahi scored the second goal shortly after Tanzania was reduced to 10 men.
Youssef En-Nesyri scored the third goal to seal the 3-0 win.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Ibrahim Hamad fouled Ziyech to give him the chance to take a free-kick, which was saved by Tanzania's goalkeeper, Aishi Manula.
Ziyech's initial free-kick was saved, but Saïss converted the rebound.
Tanzania started with Tarryn Allarakhia of Wealdstone in attack.
Novatus Miroshi was shown a second yellow card 20 minutes from the end, reducing Tanzania to 10 men.
